snippet.title: Lucky Tower Ultimate / Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
The rumors are true: We are working on a new Lucky Tower game!

https://www.slashyslashy.com/

A very early prototype is going to be released for Gamescom 2021 and is playable via Steam.

Wishlist us on Steam!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1700270/Lucky_Tower_Ultimate

Join the Discord fun:
https://discord.gg/nGkr4kqV68
